        <abstract>
            <p>Will write again to Tyndall about odours.</p> 
<p>Asks for the circumstances under which WO saw a man arrested for murder; quotes from notes he made from WO’s conversation [<hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, p. 294].</p>  
<p>Also would like to quote WO on the expression of resignation by persons about to undergo serious operations [<hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, p. 271].</p> 
        </abstract>
